 got &lt;/text&gt;&lt;val id="score"/&gt;&lt;text&gt; out of &lt;/text&gt;&lt;val id="total"/&gt;&lt;text&gt; correct.&lt;/text&gt;</multiAnswerFeedback_xml><markedFeedback_xml>&lt;text&gt;You got &lt;/text&gt;&lt;val id="percent"/&gt;&lt;text&gt;% for this marked interaction.&lt;/text&gt;</markedFeedback_xml><showPrefix>false</showPrefix><prefixActivityLevel>false</prefixActivityLevel><prefixStartIndex /><showPrefixes>false</showPrefixes><blankMinWidth>120</blankMinWidth><blankMaxWidth>650</blankMaxWidth><question_xml><question ignorePunctuation="true" ignoreCase="true"><ignoreCaseExceptIPronoun>true</ignoreCaseExceptIPronoun><ignorePunctuationWithExceptions>true</ignorePunctuationWithExceptions><text>When I arrived she [was having] &lt;b&gt; &lt;/b&gt; (&lt;b&gt;have&lt;/b&gt;) &lt;b&gt; &lt;/b&gt; a cup of coffee and she immediately asked her assistant to bring me one too.</text><label /><audioURL>learning_objects/assets/extra_aud_u016_ex2_q1.mp3</audioURL><skipPrefix>false</skipPrefix><isExample>false</isExample><modelAnswerString>When I arrived she &lt;b&gt;was having&lt;/b&gt; a cup of coffee and she immediately asked her assistant to bring me one too.</modelAnswerString></question><question ignorePunctuation="false" ignoreCase="false"><ignoreCaseExceptIPronoun>false</ignoreCaseExceptIPronoun><ignorePunctuationWithExceptions>false</ignorePunctuationWithExceptions><text>She didn't look like a film star â€“ she [was wearing] &lt;b&gt; &lt;/b&gt; (&lt;b&gt;wear&lt;/b&gt;) &lt;b&gt; &lt;/b&gt; a T-shirt and jeans, and no make-up.</text><label /><audioURL>learning_objects/assets/extra_aud_u016_ex2_q2.mp3</audioURL><skipPrefix>false</skipPrefix><isExample>false</isExample><modelAnswerString>She didn't look like a film star - she &lt;b&gt;was wearing&lt;/b&gt; a T-shirt and jeans, and no make-up.</modelAnswerString></question><question ignorePunctuation="true" ignoreCase="true"><ignoreCaseExceptIPronoun>true</ignoreCaseExceptIPronoun><ignorePunctuationWithExceptions>